    Calibration curve: 校准曲线
    Classification accuracy: 分类准确率
    F1: true
    Sensitivity and specificity: 灵敏度与特异度
    sens: 灵敏度
    spec: 特异度
    # Tule puščam TP, TN in tako naprej. Moremo to kako prevesti?
    '<p><b>Sensitivity</b> (falling) is the proportion of correctly ': <p><b>灵敏度</b>（递减）是正确检测到的正例占全部正例的比例，
    detected positive instances (TP&nbsp;/&nbsp;P).</p>: TP&nbsp;/&nbsp;P。</p>
    '<p><b>Specificity</b> (rising) is the proportion of detected ': <p><b>特异度</b>（递增）是正确检测到的负例占全部负例的比例，
    negative instances (TN&nbsp;/&nbsp;N).</p>: TN&nbsp;/&nbsp;N。</p>
    Precision and recall: 精确率与召回率
    prec: 精确率
    recall: 召回率
    '<p><b>Precision</b> (rising) is the fraction of retrieved instances ': <p><b>精确率</b>（递增）是检索到的相关实例占全部检索实例的比例，
    that are relevant, TP&nbsp;/&nbsp;(TP&nbsp;+&nbsp;FP).</p>: TP&nbsp;/&nbsp;(TP&nbsp;+&nbsp;FP)。</p>
    '<p><b>Recall</b> (falling) is the proportion of discovered relevant ': <p><b>召回率</b>（递减）是发现的相关实例占全部相关实例的比例，
    instances, TP&nbsp;/&nbsp;P.</p>: TP&nbsp;/&nbsp;P。</p>
    Pos and neg predictive value: 正预测值与负预测值
    PPV: true
    TPV: true
    '<p><b>Positive predictive value</b> (rising) is the proportion of ': <p><b>正预测值</b>（递增）是预测为正例中实际为正例的比例，
    correct positives, TP&nbsp;/&nbsp;(TP&nbsp;+&nbsp;FP).</p>: TP&nbsp;/&nbsp;(TP&nbsp;+&nbsp;FP)。</p>
    '<p><b>Negative predictive value</b> is the proportion of correct ': <p><b>负预测值</b>（递增）是预测为负例中实际为负例的比例，
    negatives, TN&nbsp;/&nbsp;(TN&nbsp;+&nbsp;FN).</p>: TN&nbsp;/&nbsp;(TN&nbsp;+&nbsp;FN)。</p>
    True and false positive rate: 真正例率与假正例率
    TPR: true
    FPR: true
    '<p><b>True and false positive rate</b> are proportions of detected ': <p><b>真正例率与假正例率</b>分别是检测到的正例与遗漏的正例
    and omitted positive instances</p>: 在所有正例或负例中的比例。</p>
